# Licious AI Protein Meal Planner

An AI-powered meal planning and pre-order assistant built for [Licious](https://www.licious.in/) — India's leading meat and seafood brand. The app 
helps users plan their weekly protein intake based on personal health goals and auto-builds an optimised Licious cart.

**Live App:** [meal-prep-guide-3.preview.emergentagent.com](https://meal-prep-guide-3.preview.emergentagent.com)

---

## What It Does

1. **Onboards the user** — collects age, weight, height, goal (weight loss / gain / muscle), and protein preference (meat, chicken, eggs)
2. **Calculates daily calorie and protein targets** — personalised to each user's body metrics and goal
3. **Plans a weekly meal schedule** — distributes protein across meals with zero wastage
4. **Builds a Licious cart** — selects the right product SKUs, pack sizes, and quantities based on the weekly plan

